OL,3,CNI Water needs funded correctly says
OL,4,CUtility Regulator
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland Water needs to be
OL,7,Ffunded correctly, the Utility
OL,8,FRegulator chief has said.
OL,10,FThe company that runs the region's
OL,11,Fwater and wastewater services has been
OL,12,Fdescribed as chronically underfunded.
OL,14,FLast month a report by the Audit
OL,15,FOffice said NI Water has struggled to
OL,16,Fsecure adequate funding for
OL,17,Finfrastructure upgrades since it was
OL,18,Festablished in 2007.
