OL,3,CNI Water needs funded correctly says
OL,4,CUtility Regulator
OL,6,FIt recommended a comprehensive expert
OL,7,Freview of how NI Water is funded and
OL,8,Fgoverned.
OL,10,FThe Assembly earlier this week debated
OL,11,Fa motion on whether NI Water should be
OL,12,Fmutualised.
OL,14,FThen, Infrastructure Minister John
OL,15,FO'Dowd voiced his opposition to
OL,16,Fmutualisation, contending it will lead
OL,17,Fto domestic water charges which he has
OL,18,Fruled out introducing.
