OL,6,FHe said public infrastructure has been
OL,7,Funderfunded for many years, adding the
OL,8,FExecutive is currently pressing the UK
OL,9,Fgovernment for further funding for
OL,10,Fpublic services.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Utility Regulator chief
OL,13,Fexecutive John French said the funding
OL,14,Fmust be sorted before the type of
OL,15,Fmanagement model for the company is
OL,16,Flooked at.
