OL,6,FGiving evidence to the Assembly
OL,7,Fscrutiny committee for the Department
OL,8,Ffor Infrastructure, Mr French
OL,9,Fdescribed the situation as having gone
OL,10,Fon for a long time, noting a report in
OL,11,F2007 that said water services were
OL,12,Funderfunded.
OL,14,FAs well as regulating gas and
OL,15,Felectricity prices in Northern
OL,16,FIreland, the Utility Regulator also
OL,17,Fplays a role as an economic regulator
OL,18,Ffor water services.
