OL,6,FMr French said everyone, including the
OL,7,Fdepartment, is in a difficult position
OL,8,Fwhen it comes to NI Water.
OL,10,F"Nobody wants to be in this position.
OL,11,FThis has been going on for a long
OL,12,Ftime," he told the committee.
OL,14,F"If you look back at the reports back
OL,15,Fin 2007, the Water Service was
OL,16,Funderfunded then.
OL,18,F"Essentially the capital spending is
OL,19,F40% less than what it needs to be to
OL,20,Fachieve the wastewater targets.
