OL,6,F"Either you dilute what is asked of NI
OL,7,FWater or you provide them the funding."
OL,9,FAsked about the potential of a
OL,10,Fdifferent management model for NI
OL,11,FWater, Mr French said the ownership
OL,12,Fmodel is a political decision.
OL,14,F"What we're looking for is to make
OL,15,Fsure that Northern Ireland Water is
OL,16,Fcorrectly funded," he said.
